Title: Will You Marry Monk?
Director: Weeravat Chayochaikon, Ongart Cheamcharoenpornkul, Voravuth Thawinwisitwat
Writer: Juttuporn Boothkort, Weeravat Chayochaikon, Phairat Thaton
Actors: Pae Arak Amornsupasiri, Patara Eksangkul, Kornnaphat Sethratanapong
Plot: A Thai monk heads to his sister's wedding in Japan, but grows concerned when he learns about her groom's dark past. As he tries to prevent their union, the former gangster must demonstrate he's truly changed.
